{"type":"wb","version":2,"source":"https://www.iodraw.com","elements":[{"type":"text","version":1256,"versionNonce":325680641,"isDeleted":false,"id":"GoNi4S6-IT88OXvHijiOE","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":368.1817932128906,"y":149.1818084716797,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":795,"height":265,"seed":717012085,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"sharp","boundElements":[],"updated":1776412318863,"link":null,"fontSize":16,"fontFamily":2,"text":"当前黑洞引擎的交互编辑逻辑中，把场景编辑分为编辑状态和查看状态，当时考虑分开的原因如下：\n主要原因：\n1. 场景编辑涉及到位置配准，而做了HLOD的BIM资源中单个构件不具备编辑位置的能力，但具备被选中的能力；\n2. 单构件在部署时是通过单构件资源包创建实例，但是这样的单个资源包需要在实际浏览中优化合并；\n次要原因：\n1. 场景编辑状态中，矢量数据集在加入场景时需要根据场景坐标系进行瓦片化切分，这个转换涉及排队等待；\n2. 把编辑、添加等改变场景的操作 跟查看、查询、测量剖切等使用场景的操作分开，更清晰些；\n\n现在面临的问题：\n有用户认为，现在必须在场景编辑态\n随后的开发计划中，会增加动画编辑功能，\n","baseline":261,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"当前黑洞引擎的交互编辑逻辑中，把场景编辑分为编辑状态和查看状态，当时考虑分开的原因如下：\n主要原因：\n1. 场景编辑涉及到位置配准，而做了HLOD的BIM资源中单个构件不具备编辑位置的能力，但具备被选中的能力；\n2. 单构件在部署时是通过单构件资源包创建实例，但是这样的单个资源包需要在实际浏览中优化合并；\n次要原因：\n1. 场景编辑状态中，矢量数据集在加入场景时需要根据场景坐标系进行瓦片化切分，这个转换涉及排队等待；\n2. 把编辑、添加等改变场景的操作 跟查看、查询、测量剖切等使用场景的操作分开，更清晰些；\n\n现在面临的问题：\n有用户认为，现在必须在场景编辑态\n随后的开发计划中，会增加动画编辑功能，\n"},{"type":"image","version":196,"versionNonce":1794025307,"isDeleted":false,"id":"tghPpZoOXWxxkE3mVTH6i","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":1340.3580299270095,"y":644.363655090332,"strokeColor":"transparent","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":721.6475972540046,"height":438,"seed":506956923,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"round","boundElements":[],"updated":1776220253602,"link":null,"status":"saved","fileId":"f3471cb842709fdcf3d2e71a54fe0128550d7e46","scale":[1,1]},{"type":"image","version":194,"versionNonce":87862741,"isDeleted":false,"id":"3vgo5Iuaq5p-Ewp9lJgC1","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":1341.1740731301309,"y":190.4545786045802,"strokeColor":"transparent","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":720.9243243243244,"height":438,"seed":1456918107,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"round","boundElements":[],"updated":1776220243754,"link":null,"status":"saved","fileId":"b93fcf21a8abf2bb59749a61a9b1b1421134dd18","scale":[1,1]}],"appState":{"theme":"light","currentChartType":"bar","currentItemBackgroundColor":"transparent","currentItemEndArrowhead":"arrow","currentItemFillStyle":"hachure","currentItemFontFamily":2,"currentItemFontSize":16,"currentItemLinearStrokeSharpness":"round","currentItemOpacity":100,"currentItemRoughness":1,"currentItemStartArrowhead":null,"currentItemStrokeColor":"#000000","currentItemStrokeSharpness":"sharp","currentItemStrokeStyle":"solid","currentItemStrokeWidth":1,"currentItemTextAlign":"left","cursorButton":"up","editingGroupId":null,"elementLocked":false,"elementType":"selection","exportBackground":true,"exportScale":1,"exportEmbedScene":false,"exportWithDarkMode":false,"gridSize":null,"lastPointerDownWith":"mouse","name":"Untitled-2026-04-15-0945","openMenu":null,"previousSelectedElementIds":{"GoNi4S6-IT88OXvHijiOE":true,"4TgrUpOwmDzb7EosMaemn":true,"YXSLluaW1NNQJackSALGm":true},"scrolledOutside":false,"scrollX":59.954559326171875,"scrollY":166.5908966064453,"selectedElementIds":{},"selectedGroupIds":{},"shouldCacheIgnoreZoom":false,"showStats":false,"viewBackgroundColor":"#fff9db","zenModeEnabled":false,"zoom":{"value":1}},"files":{"f3471cb842709fdcf3d2e71a54fe0128550d7e46":{"mimeType":"image/png","id":"f3471cb842709fdcf3d2e71a54fe0128550d7e46","dataURL":"data:image/png;base64,","created":1776220192128},"b93fcf21a8abf2bb59749a61a9b1b1421134dd18":{"mimeType":"image/png","id":"b93fcf21a8abf2bb59749a61a9b1b1421134dd18","dataURL":"data:image/png;base64,","created":1776220201862}}}